Vim Completion kind
-------------------

- <C-P>: keyword completion

- insert mode

  - <C-X> + key
  - http://www.openfoundry.org/en/tech-column/2215
  - key

    - <C-l>: line completion
    - <C-i>: keyword completion (also search include file)
    - <C-n>: keyword completion (single file)

    - <C-d>: definition and macro
    - <C-f>: filename
    - <C-]>: tag file
    - <C-k>: dictionary file
    - <C-t>: Thesaurus completion, like dictionary.

    - <C-o>: call omnifunc
    - <C-u>: call completefunc
    - <C-v>: vim command

    - <C-e>: ?
    - <C-p>: ?
    - <C-y>: ?

C Plugins
---------
- ctags incremental
- cscope incremental

  - 當你的 source code 有改變或是新增加檔案，你就要將新增加的檔案加入到 cscope.files (步驟3)，
    然後再次重新 build 你的 database(步驟4).
    http://hamisme.blogspot.tw/search/label/Cscope%20and%20Ctags

- tags in database instead of plain file

  - https://github.com/xuhdev/tags2db
  - CodeLite: http://www.wikiwand.com/en/CodeLite

- OmniCppComplete

  - 2 backend

    1. ctags
    2. ClangComplete
